Multiple comparisons between mean accuracies of OneR, JRip and PART models for IAV virulence based on two-class and three-class BALB/C, C57BL/6, H1N1, H3N2 and H5N1 datasets containing either the concatenated alignment of all IAV proteins or an individual alignment of PB2, PB1, PA, HA, NP, NA, M1, NS1, PB1-F2, PA-X, M2 and NS2 proteins.
